<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When setting a logger for {{Zend_Translate}}, we can set a {{Zend_Log}} instance, a custom log message but not a custom a priority.</p>

<p>By default, {{Zend_Translate_Adapter}}, use the {{notice}} priority level, but in our application such 'notice' are almost useful only for debug because i18n is not a critical part of it.</p>

<p>Another use case would be if we want to use {{Zend_Log_Filter}} to selectively log our messages in a separate {{Zend_Log_Writer}}</p>

